formerly of Global Election Systems, Diebold Election Systems and Election Systems &amp; Software.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Clear Ballot ClearCast is a digital scan paper ballot tabulator designed for use at the polling place. After a voter marks a paper ballot, her ballot is inserted into the unit for processing. The tabulator uses high speed, high resolution, commercial scan engines to simultaneously image the front and back of the ballot. The resulting ballot images are processed by the Intel NUC, an off the shelf miniature PC, which identifies and evaluates marks made by the voter.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":"","_links_to":"","_links_to_target":""},"categories":[],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2285","election-system","type-election-system","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","description-off"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/election-system\/2285"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/election-system"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/election-system"}],"version-history":[{"count":37,"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/election-system\/2285\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":14135,"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/election-system\/2285\/revisions\/14135"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2285"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2285"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2285"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}